headline: Oracle Named a Leader in Configure, Price, Quote by Independent Research Firm
summary: Oracle has been named a Leader in The Forrester Wave™: Configure, Price, Quote Solutions, Q1 2025 report for Oracle Fusion Cloud Configure, Price, Quote (CPQ), part of Oracle Fusion Cloud Customer Experience (CX). The report evaluated 13 vendors and named Oracle Cloud CPQ as one of four Leaders, giving Oracle the highest score in the Strategy categories. A copy of the report is available here.
